quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Toaa – Siin -- Miim
  26,2,Woi yε Nsεm a efri Nwoma pefee no mu
  26,3,Ebia wo (de awerεhoͻ) bekum wo ho sε wͻ’nnyε agyidiefoͻ nti
  26,4,Sε Yε’pε a anka Yε’besiane nsεnkyerεnee bi fri soro aba wͻn so a εbεma wͻn kͻn aberε ase wͻ ahobraseε mu
  26,5,Afutusεm foforͻ biara a ebefri Ahummͻborͻ Hene no hͻ aba wͻn hͻ no gyesε wͻ’twi fa so
  26,6,Ampa sε wͻn apo (Asεm no); deε wͻ’dii ho fεw no ho asεm bεba wͻn so
  26,7,Anaasε wͻ’nhunuu nneεma papa ahodoͻ a Yε’ma no fifiri wͻ asaase no soͻ
  26,8,"Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wͻn mu pii nye nni"
  26,9,"Nokorε sε wo Wura Nyankopͻn, Ɔne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"
  26,10,"Kae εberε a wo Wura Nyankopͻn frεε Mose (ka kyerεε no) sε: “Kͻ amanfoͻ abͻneεfoͻ no hͻ"
  26,11,Farao nkorͻfoͻ no. Enti wͻ’nnsuro Nyame?”
  26,12,"Mose kaa sε: ”Me Wura, mesuro sε wͻ’bεbu me ͻtorofo “"
  26,13,"M’akoma nso sua, na mekεtrεma nso ntumi nkasa yie, enti soma Aaron (ma no ne me nkͻ)"
  26,14,"Na (Farao ne nenkorͻfoͻ) wͻ (awudisεm ho) bͻne bi tia me, enti mesuro sε wͻ’beku me”"
  26,15,"(Nyankopͻn) kaa sε: ”Ɛmma saa da. Mo mmienu monfa Yε’nsεnkyerεnee nkͻ. Nokorε sε, Yε’ka moho, Yε’te“"
  26,16,"Enti mo mmienu monkͻ Farao hͻ na monka sε: “Nokorε, yε’yε Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no asomafoͻ"
  26,17,Na ma Israel mma no ne yεn nkͻ
  26,18,"Farao kaa sε: “Ɛnyε yεn mu ha ara na yεtetee wo ԑberԑ a woyԑ akͻdaa? Ɛna wode wo mfie pii tenaa yεn mu ha"
  26,19,"Ɛna woyεε wo neyεε a woyͻeε, εna wo kͻkaa boniayεfoͻ no ho “"
  26,20,"(Mose) kaa sε: “Meyεε no wͻ εberε a na meka wͻn a wayera no ho “"
  26,21,"“Enti medwane frii mohͻ wͻ aberε a na mesuro mo; enti me Wura Nyankopͻn adom ama me adwen, εna Ɔde me aka asomafoͻ no ho “"
  26,22,“Woi ne adom a wode adom me a wodeka m’anim sε wode Israel mma ayε nkoa? “
  26,23,"Farao kaa sε: ”Hwan ne Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no?”"
  26,24,"Mose kaa sε: (Ɔne) ͻsoro ne asaase ne deε εwͻ ne mmienu ntεm no Wura no, sε moadwen si mopi a"
  26,25,"Farao ka kyerεε wͻn a wͻ’atwa neho ahyia no sε: “Moante? “"
  26,26,"Mose kaa sε: (Ɔne) mo Wura Nyankopͻn, ne moagyanom tetefoͻ no Wura Nyankopͻn no"
  26,27,"Farao kaa sε: “Nokorε sε mosomafoͻ no a yεsomaa no mo hͻ no abͻ dam paa “"
  26,28,"Mose kaa sε: “Apueε ne atͻeε ne deε εwͻ ne mmienu no ntεm no Wura Nyankopͻn no, sε mowͻ adwen ampa a”"
  26,29,"(Farao) kaa sε: ”(Mose), sε wofa nyame foforͻ bi ka meho a, ampa sε mede wo bεka wͻn a wͻ’da afiaseε no ho “"
  26,30,"Mose kaa sε: ”Nasε mede biribi pefee bi berε wo mpo a?”"
  26,31,"Farao kaa sε: “Ɛneε fabra, sε woka nokorεfoͻ no ho ampa a”"
  26,32,"Enti Mose too nepoma no (too fᴐm) na hwε, ͻwͻ pefee bi nie"
  26,33,"Oyii nensa na hwε, na ayε fitaa dema obi a ohunu"
  26,34,"Farao ka kyerεε nhemfo a atwa neho ahyia no sε :”Nokorε sε, woi yε nkoyaayini a onim de"
  26,35,"Ɔpε sε ͻde nekonyaa no beyi mo fri moasaase no soͻ, enti deεn na morehyε, (anaasε modwen sεn)?”"
  26,36,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Ma ͻne ne nua no ntwεn, na soma dawubͻfoͻ ma wͻ’nkכ nkuro so"
  26,37,Wᴐ’de nkoyaayifoͻ a wͻn aben paa na wͻ’nim de nyinaa bԑbrε wo”
  26,38,Enti nkoyaayifoͻ no behyiaa wͻ εda a wahyε a wͻ’nim no mu
  26,39,"Wͻ’ka kyerεε amanfoͻ no sε: “Mo (nyinaa) moahyia?”"
  26,40,”Sεdeε yεbedi (Farao) nkoyaayifoͻ no akyi sε εkͻba sε wͻ’di nkonim a”
  26,41,"Enti εberε a nkoyaayifoͻ no baeε no, wͻ’ka kyerεε Farao sε: “Sε εkͻba sε yedi nkonim a yε’benya akatua bi anaa?”"
  26,42,"Farao kaa sε: “Aane, εno deε na εyε nokorε sε mobεka wͻn a wͻ’bεn (me) no ho”"
  26,43,"Mose ka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Monto deε mobεtoͻ”"
  26,44,"Enti wͻ’too wͻn nhoma ne wͻn mpoma too fᴐm, na wͻ’kaa sε: “Farao tumi mu nti yεn na yεbedi nkonim!”"
  26,45,"Enti Mose nso too ne poma no na hwε, εmemeneee wͻn atorͻsεm a w’abͻ wͻn trim ayε no (nyinaa)"
  26,46,Enti nkoyaayifoͻ no kͻͻ fͻm de wͻn anim butuu fͻm (maa Nyankopͻn)
  26,47,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Y’agye abͻdeε nyinaa Wura Nyankopͻn no adi"
  26,48,Mose ne Aaron Wura Nyankopͻn no
  26,49,"(Farao) kaa sε: “Moadikan agye no adi aberε a menya maa mo ho kwan? Nokorε sε, (Mose) ne mo panin a ͻkyerεε mo nkoyaa yie! Mobehunu. Metwitwa monsa ne monan abͻ no abira, na m’abͻ monyinaa asennua mu“"
  26,50,"Nkoyaayifoͻ no kaa sε: “Ɛnsεe hwee! Nokorε sε ye’Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na yεbεsan akͻ”"
  26,51,"Nokorε, yε’wͻ awerεhyem sε, ye’Wura Nyankopͻn de yεn mfomsoͻ bεkyε yεn sε yεn ne nnipa a wͻn adikan agye adie “"
  26,52,"Y’eyi kyerεε Mose sε: ”Fa Menkoa no tu kwan no anadwo, na nokorε sε (Farao ne nenkorͻfoͻ) beti mo”"
  26,53,Enti Farao somaa dawubͻfoͻ kͻͻ nkuro no so
  26,54,"Sε: ”Nokorε sε saa nkorͻfoͻ yi yε dͻm kakraa bi"
  26,55,"Nanso nokorε sε, wͻ’hyε yεn abufuo"
  26,56,Nokorε sε yε’yε ɛdͻm a yεdͻͻso na y’ada yεn ho so
  26,57,Enti Ye’yii wͻn frii turo ne nsuo aniwa ho
  26,58,Ne ahonyadeε ne animuonyam gyina berε (biara) mu
  26,59,"Saa ara, na Yε’maa Israel mma no bedii wͻn adeε"
  26,60,Enti wͻ’tii wͻn wͻ εberε a na awia apue
  26,61,"Ԑberε a εdͻm mmienu no hunuu wͻn ho no, Mose nkorͻfoͻ no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε, (Farao ne nedͻm yi) bεto yεn “"
  26,62,"Mose kaa sε: “Ɛmma saa da! Nokorε sε, Me Wura Nyankopͻn ka me ho, Ɔbεkyerε me kwan “"
  26,63,"Enti Yeyi kyerεε Mose sε: “Fa wo poma no bͻ ͻpo no mu “. Na emu kyekyεe, na ne nkyekyεmu no mu biara bεyεε sε bepͻ kεseε bi"
  26,64,Enti Yε’de ekuo baako no (Farao nkorͻfoͻ) no bεn saa bea hͻ
  26,65,Na Yε’gyee Mose ne wͻn a wͻ’ka neho no nyinaa nkwa
  26,66,Afei Yε’maa nsuo faa (ekuo) baako no
  26,67,"Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wͻn mu dodoͻ no ara na wͻ’nnye nnie"
  26,68,"Nokorε sε wo Wura Nyankopͻn no Ɔne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Ahummͻborͻ Hene no"
  26,69,Kenkan Abraham nso ho asεm no kyerε wͻn
  26,70,"Ɛberε a ͻka kyerεε nepapa ne nenkorͻfoͻ no sε: “Ԑdeεn na moresom yi?”"
  26,71,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Yε’som abosom, na yε’bεkͻso de yεn ho ama wͻn”"
  26,72,"(Abraham) kaa sε: ”Enti sε mosufrε wͻn a wͻ’tie mo?”"
  26,73,Anaasε monya wͻn ho mfasoͻ anaasε ͻhaw bi?”
  26,74,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Daabi, nanso yε’bεtoo y’agya nom sε saa ara na na wͻ’reyε”"
  26,75,"(Abraham) kaa sε: “ Enti moahunu deε mosom"
  26,76,Mone moagya nom tetefoͻ no
  26,77,"Nokorε sε, wͻ’yε m’atamfo, gyesε Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura Nyankopͻn no"
  26,78,"(Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura) no a Ɔbͻͻ me, Ɔno na ͻkyerε me kwan"
  26,79,"Ɔno na Ɔma me aduane die, na Ɔma me nsuo nom"
  26,80,Sε meyare a Ɔno na Ɔsa me yadeε
  26,81,Ɔno na Ɔbεma me awuo na afei W’asan anyane me (afri owuo mu)
  26,82,Ɔno na me wͻ anidaasoͻ sε Ɔde memfomsoͻ bεkyε me wͻ Akatua da no mu
  26,83,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn, mame nyansa, adwen ne nteaseε, na fa me ka apapafoͻ no ho"
  26,84,Na ma nkyirimma no mmͻ me din pa
  26,85,Na fa me ka wͻn a wͻ’bedi adeε wͻ anigyeε Aheman no mu no ho
  26,86,"Na fa m’agya bͻne kyε no, nokorε sε ͻka ayerafoͻ no ho"
  26,87,Na engu m’anim ase wͻ Wusͻreε da
  26,88,Ɛda no a sika anaa ahonyadeԑ ne mma ho mma mfasoͻ no
  26,89,"Gyesε obia ͻde akoma pa, anaa akoma a emu teε bεba Nyankopͻn hͻ no"
  26,90,Na yε’de Aheman no bεbεn Nyamesurofoͻ no
  26,91,Na yεbeyi Amanehunu gya no adi akyerε ayerafoͻ no
  26,92,"Yԑ’bԑka akyerε wͻn sε: “Deε na mosom no wͻ hen"
  26,93,"(Deε na mo) fri Nyankopͻn akyi (som wͻn no)? Wͻ’betumi aboa mo, anaasε wͻ’betumi aboa wͻn ara wͻn ho?”"
  26,94,Na yε’bεto wͻn (abosom) no ne ayerafoͻ no ama wͻ’de wͻn ti adikan akͻ (Ogya no) mu
  26,95,Ne ͻbonsam asafo no nyinaa
  26,96,Ɛberε a wͻ’bεko wͻ (Ogya no) mu no wͻ’bεka sε
  26,97,"“Yε’dͻ Nyame sε, na yεwͻ ͻyera pefee mu"
  26,98,Ɛberε a yεde mo totoo Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no ho no
  26,99,"Ɛnyε obi na ɔyeraa yɛn, na mmom abͻneεfoͻ no ara na wͻ’maa yε’yeraeε"
  26,100,Enti seesei yenni otwitwagyefoͻ biara
  26,101,Anaa yͻnkoͻ brεboͻ
  26,102,"Sε yεrenya kwan asan akͻ y’akyi (wͻ wiase) bio a, anka yεbεka agyidiefoͻ no ho"
  26,103,"Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wᴐn mu dodoͻ no ara nnye nni"
  26,104,"Nokorε sε wo Wura Nyankopᴐn ne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Ahummͻborͻ Hene no"
  26,105,Noa nkorͻfoɔ no annye asomafoͻ no anni
  26,106,"Ɛberε a wͻn nua Noa ka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Enti monnsuro Nyankopͻn na monnyε ahwεyie"
  26,107,Nokorε sε meyε (Nyankopͻn) Somafoͻ nokwafoͻ ma mo
  26,108,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie ma me
  26,109,"Memmisa (nsεmpa a mereka kyerε mo no) ho akatua, na mmom m’akatua deε εwͻ Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura Nyankopͻn no hͻ"
  26,110,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie ma me.”
  26,111,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Yεnye wo nni wͻ aberε a (nnipa mu) mpapahwekwa a wͻ’nni mmu na wͻ’di w’akyire?”"
  26,112,"Noa kaa sε: “Ɛdeεn nimdeε na mewͻ wͻ deε wͻ’yε ho"
  26,113,"Wͻn akontabuo deε me Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na εwͻ, sε monim ampa a"
  26,114,Medeε (Menni ho tumi sε) mεpamo agyidiefoͻ no
  26,115,"Medeε nokorε (m’adwuma) nesε, meyε kͻkͻbͻni pefee”"
  26,116,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Noa, sε woanyae (wofrε no a) nokorε sε wobεka wͻn a yesi wͻn aboͻ (ku wͻn) no ho"
  26,117,"(Noa) kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, menkorͻfoͻ no abu me ͻtorofoᴐ"
  26,118,"Enti bu me ne wͻn ntεm atεn, na gye me ne agyidiefoͻ no a wͻ’ka meho no (fri abͻneεfoͻ no nsam.)”"
  26,119,Enti Yε’gyee no ne wͻn a wͻ’ka neho no nkwa wͻ nsuom hyεn a ayε mma no mu
  26,120,Afei Yε’maa nsuo faa nkaeε no
  26,121,"Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wɔ woi mu, nanso wᴐn mu dodoͻ no ara nnye nni"
  26,122,"ᴐNokorε ampa sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn, Ɔne Otumfoͻ a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"
  26,123,Aadfoͻ no annye asomafoͻ no anni
  26,124,"Ɛberε a wͻn nua Huud ka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Adεn monnsuro Nyame"
  26,125,"Nokorε sε, meyε Ɔsomafoͻ nokwafoͻ ma mo"
  26,126,Enti monsuro Nyame na monyε sotie ma me
  26,127,"Memmisa mo (nsεmpa a mereka kyerε mo no) ho akatua, na mmom m’akatua deε εwͻ Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ"
  26,128,Mosisi adan akεseε wͻ mea mea a εhͻ korͻn wͻ akwan ho degye moani kwa (wͻ aberε a montena mu)
  26,129,Mosisi aban soroͻ a εyε fε nso ma moho tesε deε mobεtena mu afe bͻͻ
  26,130,"Sε mosͻ (obi mu anaasε monsa ka obi a), mosͻ ne mu anaasε mone no di no wͻ atrimuͻden so"
  26,131,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie mame
  26,132,Monsuro Nea Ɔde deε monim no adom mo
  26,133,Ɔde nyεmmoa ne mma adom mo
  26,134,Ne mfuo ne nsuo aniwa
  26,135,"Nokorε sε, medeε mesuro Da kεseε no asotwee no ho asεm mamo”"
  26,136,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Sε wotu yεn fo o, anaasε woanka afutufoͻ no ho o, εyε asεm korͻ ma yεn"
  26,137,Woi deε εyε tetefoͻ no suban no bia
  26,138,Yε’nntwe yεn aso biara “
  26,139,"Wͻ’buu no ͻtorofo, enti Yε’sεee wͻn. Nokorε sε nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wᴐn mu dodoͻ no ara nnye nni"
  26,140,"Nokorε ampa sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn Ɔne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"
  26,141,Samuudfoͻ buu Asomafoͻ no atorofo
  26,142,"Ɛberε a wͻn nua Soalhu ka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Adεn, monsuro Nyame"
  26,143,"Nokorε sε, meyε (Nyankopͻn) Somafoͻ nokwafoͻ dema mo"
  26,144,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie ma me
  26,145,"Memmisa mo (nsεmpa a mereka kyerε mo no) ho akatua, mmom m’akatua deε εwͻ Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ"
  26,146,Enti (modwen sε) yebegyae mo wͻ abodweԑ mu wͻ deε mo wͻ mu wͻ εha yi ho
  26,147,Wͻ turo ne nsutire mu
  26,148,Ne mfudeε ne akyiresua a εso aba a agu nhyerεnee na abͻ esa-sa
  26,149,Modwa mmepͻ mu deyε afie a moadare mu (anaa mode tu moho)
  26,150,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie mma me
  26,151,Na monhwε na moanni nsεmmͻnedifoͻ no ahyεdeε so
  26,152,Wͻn a wͻ’di nsεmmͻne wͻ asaase no soͻ na wͻ’nntoto ntotoeε pa no “
  26,153,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Woka wͻn a konya anya wͻn no ho"
  26,154,"Woyε nipa tesε yεn ara, enti fa nsεnkyerεnee bi bra, sε woka nokorεfoͻ no ho ampa a.”"
  26,155,"(Soalhu) kaa sε: “Yoma bedeε bi nie, ͻwͻ ho kwan sε ͻnom (nsuo), ɛna monso mo wɔ ho kwan sε monom (nsuo) wͻ εda a yahyε (ama mo ne yoma no)"
  26,156,"Monhwε yie na moanyε no bͻne biara, amma asotwee ammεsͻ momu da kεseε bi “"
  26,157,"Nanso wͻ’kum no, enti wͻ’benuu wͻn ho"
  26,158,"Enti asotwee no sͻͻ wͻn mu. Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wᴐn mu dodoͻ no ara nnye nni"
  26,159,"Nokorε sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn ne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"
  26,160,Lut nkorͻfoͻ no buu asomafoͻ no atorofoᴐ
  26,161,"Ɛberε a wͻn nua Lut ka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Adεn, monsuro Nyame"
  26,162,"Nokorε sε, meyε Ɔsomafoͻ nokwafoͻ ma mo"
  26,163,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie mame
  26,164,Memmisa mo akatua (wͻ nsεmpa a mereka kyerε mo no) ho; mmom m’akatua deε εwͻ Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ
  26,165,Abͻdeε no mu no mmarima ho na mokͻ
  26,166,"Ɛna mogyae deε mo Wura Nyankopͻn abͻ ama mo a εyε moyere nom? Daabi, moyε amanfoͻ mmaratofoͻ paa“"
  26,167,"Wͻ’kaa sε: “Lut, sε w’anyae (wonsεm no ka a) wobεka wͻn a yapamo wͻn anaa yatu wͻn (afri y’asaase soͻ) no ho"
  26,168,"Ɔkaa sε: “Nokorε sε, mekyiri metan mo neyεε no"
  26,169,"Me Wura Nyankopͻn, gye me ne m’abusuafoͻ fri deε wͻ’reyε no mu “"
  26,170,Enti Yε’gyee no ne n’abusuafoͻ nyinaa
  26,171,"Gyesε (ne yere) aberewa no, ͻkaa wͻn a wͻ’kaa akyire no ho"
  26,172,Afei Yε’sεee wͻn a aka no pasaa
  26,173,Yε’tͻͻͻ nsuo (a ԑyԑ asotwee) paa de guu wͻn so. Na εyε nsutͻ bͻne paa ma wͻn a yεbͻͻ wͻn kͻkͻ no
  26,174,"Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wᴐn mu dodoͻ no ara nnye nni"
  26,175,"Nokorε sε wo Wura Nyankopͻn ne Otumfoͻ no a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"
  26,176,Na Aikatfoͻ no buu asomafoͻ no atorofoͻ
  26,177,"Ɛberε a Shu’aib ka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Adεn, monsuro Nyame"
  26,178,"Nokorε sε, meyε Ɔsomafoͻ nokwafoͻ ma mo"
  26,179,Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie ma me
  26,180,"Memmisa mo (nsεmpa a mereka kyerε mo no ho) akatua, mmom m’akatua deε εwͻ Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ"
  26,181,"Monhyε (biribiara) ma no nyε mma, na monhwε yie na moammͻ (amanfoͻ) nyansa korͻno"
  26,182,Monfa nsanea a εtenee na ensusu (adeε ma amanfoͻ)
  26,183,Monhwε na moanfa nyansa (korͻno kwan so) ante amanfoͻ nneεma so (ansisi wͻn) amma nsεmmͻnee annkͻso wͻ asaase no so
  26,184,Na monsuro Nyankopͻn no a Ɔbͻͻ mo ne awoͻ ntotoasoͻ a edii kan no “
  26,185,"Wͻ’kaa sε: ”Wodeε woka wͻn a konya anya wͻn no ho"
  26,186,"Woyε onipa tesε yεn ara, na yεn deε yε’dwene sε woka nkontompofoͻ no ho"
  26,187,Enti sε woyε nokwafoͻ ampa a εneε ma ͻsoro no mu sini bi mmu megu yεn so“
  26,188,"Ɔkaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn nim dwuma a modie no (nyinaa) “"
  26,189,"Wͻ’buu no ᴐtorofoᴐ, enti asotwee sͻͻ wͻn mu wͻ Enyunu da anaa Esum da bi mu. Nokorε sε na εyε asotwee kεseε Da"
  26,190,"Nokorε sε, nsεnkyerεnee wͻ woi mu, nanso wᴐn mu dodoͻ no ara nnye nni"
  26,191,"Wo Wura Nyankopͻn, Ɔne Otumfoͻ a Otumi ade nyinaa yε, Ɔne Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"
  26,192,Nokorε sε (Qur’aan yi) yε Adiyisεm a efri Abͻdeε nyinaa Wura no hͻ
  26,193,Honhom Nokwafoͻ no (Gabriel) na ͻde siane
  26,194,"baa w’akoma mu, sεdeε wobεka akͻkͻbͻfoͻ no ho"
  26,195,Wͻ Arab kasa pefee no mu
  26,196,"Nokorε sε, (Qur’aan yi, ne Nkͻmhyεni Muhammad ho asεm) wͻ Nyamesεm Nwoma a edii kan (Tawra ne Injeel) no mu"
  26,197,Enti εnyε nsεnkyerεnee mma Quraishfoᴐ no sε Israel mu nwomanimfoͻ no nim yie (sε Qur’aan ho nkͻmhyε wͻ Tawra ne Injeel no mu)
  26,198,Sε Ye’sianee (Qur’aan yi) maa obi a ͻnnyε Arabni mpo–
  26,199,"Ɛna ͻrekenkan kyerε wͻn a, anka wͻ’nnye nni"
  26,200,Saa ara na Yε’ma (gye a wͻ’nnye Qur’aan nnie) no wura abͻneεfoͻ no akoma mu
  26,201,Wͻ’nnye nni kͻpem sε wͻ’behunu asotwee yaaya no ansa
  26,202,Ɛbεba wͻn so mpofirem a wͻ’nnim ho hwee koraa
  26,203,"Ԑhͻ na wͻ’bεka sε: ”Enti yεmma yεn ahomegye berε?”"
  26,204,Enti Ya’sotwee na wͻ’repε no ntεm no
  26,205,"(Nkͻmhyεni), enti w’ahunu? Sε Yε’ma wͻn mfie tenten mpo a"
  26,206,Deε yahyε wͻn ho bͻ no ba wͻn so a
  26,207,(Mfi tenten a wͻ’diiε) de gyee wͻn ani no ho mma mfasoͻ biara mma wͻn
  26,208,Ya’nsεe kuro bi gyesε (Yedi kan ma) wͻ’nya kͻkͻbͻfoͻ
  26,209,De afutusεm (brԑ wᴐn); na Yεn nyεε bͻne da
  26,210,Ԑnyε abonsamfoͻ na wͻ’sianee (Qur’aan) yi
  26,211,"Na εmfata wͻn, na wͻ’ntumi mpo"
  26,212,Nokorε sε yatwe wͻn afri (Qur’aan yi) ho kͻ akyirikyiri sε wͻ’bεtie mpo
  26,213,Enti hwε na w’ansu amfrε nyame foforͻ biara anka Nyankopͻn ho na wo ankͻka wͻn a yεbεtwe wͻn aso no ho
  26,214,Na bͻ w’abusuafoͻ no a wͻ’bεn (woͻ) no nso kͻkͻ
  26,215,Na berε w’ataban ase fama agyidiefoͻ no a wͻ’di wakyire no
  26,216,"Nasε wͻ’antie wo a, ka sε: “Medeε m’atwe meho afri dwuma a modie no ho “"
  26,217,"Na fa woho to Otumfoͻ no a otumi ade nyinaa yε, Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no so"
  26,218,(Otumfoͻ) no a Ohu wo wͻ εberε a w’asͻre agyina hͻ (rebͻ mpaeε anadwo)
  26,219,Ne w’ahokeka wͻ wͻn a wͻ’de wͻn anim abutu fͻm (frε Nyame) no mu
  26,220,"Nokorε sε, Ɔne Otiefoͻ no a Ɔte biribiara, na Ɔne Onimdefoͻ no"
  26,221,Enti Menkyerε mo obia abonsamfoͻ siane ba nesoͻ
  26,222,"Wͻ’siane ba onipa biara a ͻyε nkontomponi, bͻnefoͻ no so"
  26,223,"(Nipa bͻneni no a) ͻyε aso dema (ͻbonsam), na wͻn mu dodoͻ no ara yε nkontompofoͻ"
  26,224,Na wᴐn a wᴐ’ka anwensԑm no deε ayerafoͻ no na wͻ’di wͻn akyi
  26,225,"Wonhunuu sε wͻ’di akͻneaba wͻ bonhwa biara mu, (ka biribiara ho asεm, kamfo deε εyε ne deε εnyε nyinaa wͻ anwensԑm mu)"
  26,226,Nokorԑ sԑ wͻ’ka deε wͻ’nnyε ho asεm
  26,227,"Gyesε wͻn a wͻ’agye adie na wͻ’di dwuma pa, na wͻ’kaekae Nyankopͻn (wͻ εberε) biara (mu), na wͻ’bͻ wͻn ho ban wͻ akyire yi a yasisi wͻn. Na wͻn a wͻ’yε bͻne no behunu bea korͻ a wͻ’bεdane wͻn ho akͻ"